import React from 'react'
import { Row,Form,Button } from 'react-bootstrap'

const FormInput = () => {
  return (
   <Row>
    
       
        <Form.Control type="email" placeholder="ادخل سؤال" />
        
        <Form.Control type="password" placeholder="ادخل اجابه" />
      
      <Button sm="4" className="btn btn-primary m-2" type="submit">
        اضافه
      </Button>
   
   </Row>
  )
}

export default FormInput
